<section id="technology" class="section tech-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Technology Highlights</h2>
    <div class="tech-grid">
      <div class="tech-item">
        <div class="tech-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <polyline points="8 12 12 16 16 12"></polyline>
            <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-content">
          <h3>Real-Time Tracking</h3>
          <p>Stay informed with live tracking for every delivery. Monitor your packages in real-time from pickup to delivery, giving you complete visibility and peace of mind.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-item">
        <div class="tech-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-content">
          <h3>Customer Portal & App</h3>
          <p>Seamless database access, updates, and proof of delivery at your fingertips. Our user-friendly platform gives you control over your logistics operations from any device.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tech-item">
        <div class="tech-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21.21 15.89A10 10 0 1 1 8 2.83"></path>
            <path d="M22 12A10 10 0 0 0 12 2v10z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-content">
          <h3>Customized Reporting</h3>
          <p>Gain valuable insights from site visitations and deliveries. Our detailed analytics and customizable reports help you make data-driven decisions to optimize your operations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .tech-section {
    background-color: var(--color-black);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .tech-section .section-title {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .tech-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  
  .tech-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .tech-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .tech-content h3 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .tech-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tech-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .tech-icon {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>